Scope
-----

DECUHR.jl is a translation of, and a modification of, the Fortran routines
DECHHR, DETRHR, DESBHR, DEADHR, DECALP, D132RE, D113RE, D09HRE, D07HRE,
DEINHR, DEFSHR and DERLHR described in the 1994 paper. The present Julia
implementation, together with its Integrals.jl integration layer, test suite
and documentation, is additionally covered by the MIT License recorded in
`LICENSE` (Copyright © 2026 Jean-François Barthélémy).

The MIT grant on the Julia port does not supersede the upstream notice above:
downstream users must preserve both this NOTICE file and the `LICENSE` file
in all copies and derivative works.

